  m_text: 'Simple clocks have no goals or lives. Once stopped, that''s it. Progress
    check-in is disabled.


    Clocks with goals can prompt a progress check-in
    once per day. Regardless of clock type, your progress is dependent on your honesty.
    Setting goals unlocks XP-rewards in adventure mode.'
